 nowrap><b><font color='white' face='Verdana' size='2'>Moonspark</font></b></td>
        <TD bgcolor='black' valign='top'><font color='white' face='Verdana' size='2'> Starts and ends in Ssra temple.  You have to kill four named snakes there for 4 different pieces.  One drops a ring, one drops an idol, one drops a pouch you combine it in and one drops an insignia.  I don't feel like explaining it in depth, but I'm sure someone on your server knows about this quest.  It's not a big secret really.</P><P> </font></td>
      </tr>
      <TR>
        <TD bgcolor='black' valign='top'
 nowrap><b><font color='white' face='Verdana' size='2'>Orwen</font></b></td>
        <TD bgcolor='black' valign='top'><font color='white' face='Verdana' size='2'> Basically you run around first floor killing snakes until you get a commander to spawn.  Kill him for an idol.  Go to second floor (bring a rogue to open door in assassin room) and kill more snakes until you get another commander to spawn.  Kill him for a ring.  Go to third floor and kill the general for an insignia.  Then go down to the basement and kill taskmasters until you get a pouch.  Combine idol+ring+insignia in the pouch and you get a ring of shissar.</P><P>Doesn't have to be in that order.  The general will require a couple groups, the rest can be done with one group.  The pouch is very common so you can put that off to last unless you've got plenty of space to lug a container around.</P><P> </font></td>
      </tr>
